### 1) Create a saved search
POST http://localhost:3000/api/saved-searches
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "laptop",
  "filters": { "maxPrice": 1000, "fastDelivery": true }
}

### 2) List saved searches
GET http://localhost:3000/api/saved-searches

### 3) Delete a saved search (fill id from step 2)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/saved-searches
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "<replace-with-id-from-step-2>"
}

### 4) List again (should be fewer/empty)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/saved-searches
